{"tid":1513100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[G7] 唔好再衰多次97回歸中英談判","createTime":"2019-08-28T07:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:57:28.000Z","uid":160135,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4345361b88cb160e0904ae81c2b41e3ad2667d5","tid":1513100,"uid":160135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"當時97中英談判香港人無強烈意願要歸英國，結果英國呢d民主國家無當地人起個道德高地比佢黎談判，最後點大家都知。<br />\n<br />\n反觀直布羅陀一直強烈表達親英，英國先可以出師有名幫佢地。雖然唔係蘋果對蘋果，但係都係一個啟示當地人民意願既重要性！！<br />\n<br />\n今次G7,英，美比曬貼士我地啦！要比佢地出師有名，係香港人請求佢地出手求助！將事件推離&quot;国家內政&quot;! <br />\n<br />\n大家出聲，眾籌登國際廣告，遊行絕對唔少得！！！認真好重要！！"},{"pid":"00e76c3faae4779ea71e665f4a8398df7196501e","tid":1513100,"uid":160135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f484548a072970b606c20b756af6d29795adcb74","tid":1513100,"uid":160135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e22914a8cdec88a7c1f9832d04c78db8589149b8","tid":1513100,"uid":160135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ce7e81980bf1e81bf9bc4683e273cad3c5080f85","tid":1513100,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f00102b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihk